Allied Irish Appoints Simon Ball, Thomas Wacker To Board

-- B y   J o e   B r e n n a n
-- 
2011-10-13T09:07:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/allied-irish-appoints-simon-ball-thomas-wacker-to-board.html
Allied Irish Banks Plc (ALBK)  said it
appointed Simon Ball and Thomas Wacker as non-executive
directors of the group.  Ball is currently non-executive deputy chairman of  Cable &
Wireless Communications Plc (CWC)  and a non-executive director of
 Tribal Group Plc (TRB) , the Dublin-based lender said. Wacker is non-
executive director and former Chief Executive Officer of Belmont
Advisors (U.K.) Ltd, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joe Brennan in Dublin at 
 jbrennan29@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
